reviewText:
Didn't watched the whole anime (stoped watching it after the pain big battle), the game showed me what happened after with no fillers. Like watching a Naruto quick rundown of the whole story (I belive so, not sure).

Good gameplay with simple controls and anime look alike graphics. Personally I would recommend this only if you like the anime.

/*Finished 100% the game achievements in 63 hours, you can do it in less time but there are many things you can do that aren't related to any achievement*/
